  "datePublished": "2026-03-09",
  "description": "A bust in [blackjack](../index.md) is a hand total above 21, which causes that hand to lose immediately under the standard rules [@thorp1966]. If the player busts, the dealer does not need to finish drawing. If the dealer busts after the player has stood, all remaining player hands that have not already busted win.",
